=== Summary ===
20,000 recs: size 59.54% smaller (avro vs json), encode 30.86%, decode 16.53% (positive means Avro faster)
50,000 recs: size 59.54% smaller (avro vs json), encode 42.03%, decode 16.59% (positive means Avro faster)
100,000 recs: size 59.54% smaller (avro vs json), encode 51.34%, decode 16.29% (positive means Avro faster)

